description.narrative: (Ethiopia): The USAID/Ethiopia HAPN office will buy into this OFDA mechanism. This activity will be funded through reprogrammed resources to provide emergency support for WASH to prevent the erosion of hard won gains in MNCH that have been attained with USG and broader donor support over the past decade. These funds are used to support resilience/development activities to complement OFDA and other humanitarian actor's investments to the drought.
